<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF756ACAFF5B91F81FB3B321" pageId="142" pageNumber="902" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF756ACAFF5B91F81FB3B321" blockId="142.[164,1372,1282,2146]" pageId="142" pageNumber="902">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF756ACAFF5B91F81C08BCF0" bold="true" box="[167,520,1953,1986]" pageId="142" pageNumber="902">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Virtually nothing is known about the Bismarck Woolly Bat’s ecology and threats, and additional research is needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
